WarlockLevel5Spells.Name: Contact Other Plane
WarlockLevel5Spells.Description: You mentally contact a demigod, the spirit of a long-dead sage, or some other mysterious entity from another plane.

WarlockLevel5Spells.Name: Dream
WarlockLevel5Spells.Description: This spell shapes a creature's dreams.

WarlockLevel5Spells.Name: Hold Monster
WarlockLevel5Spells.Description: Choose a creature that you can see within range.

WarlockLevel5Spells.Name: Scrying
WarlockLevel5Spells.Description: You can see and hear a particular creature you choose that is on the same plane of existence as you.
